    <item>
      <title>美国银行认为中国私营开发商缺乏资金支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-12/bofa-funding-support-for-china-poe-developers-lacking-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行全球研究部首席大中华区经济学家乔海伦讨论了中国房地产开发商的债务困境和政府政策。穆迪评级取消了国有开发商万科企业的投资级信用评级，并警告称可能会进一步下调。乔在“彭博社：中国秀”上发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-12/bofa-funding-support-for-china-poe-developers-lacking-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 03:01:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪将中国开发商万科评级下调至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-12/moody-s-cuts-china-developer-vanke-cut-to-junk-territory-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对其偿债能力的担忧日益加剧，国有开发商万科集团一直面临压力，穆迪评级将其信用评级下调至垃圾级。斯蒂芬·恩格尔在彭博电视台进行报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-12/moody-s-cuts-china-developer-vanke-cut-to-junk-territory-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 02:35:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外国基金加入看好中国的行列，重新爱上宁德时代</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/foreign-funds-join-china-bulls-to-fall-back-in-love-with-catl</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，海外投资者加入了当代新能源科技有限公司 (Contemporary Amperex Technology Co.) 的买盘狂潮，因中国遭受重创的可再生能源股票重新燃起人们的兴奋感，推动该公司股价飙升逾 14%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/foreign-funds-join-china-bulls-to-fall-back-in-love-with-catl</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 02:28:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国瓶装水巨头农夫山泉因抵制呼吁而股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-bottled-water-giant-nongfu-spring-drops-on-boycott-calls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国饮料巨头农夫山泉公司是最新一个受到大陆网络民族主义公民大军攻击的主要品牌，凸显了国内企业在日益爱国的环境中面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/china-bottled-water-giant-nongfu-spring-drops-on-boycott-calls</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 02:12:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通货膨胀降温，阿根廷出人意料地将利率下调至 80%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-cuts-rates-to-80-in-surprise-move-as-inflation-cools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷央行出人意料地将基准利率从 100% 下调至 80%，原因是政策制定者预计月度通胀降温，而平行市场上比索兑美元继续走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-cuts-rates-to-80-in-surprise-move-as-inflation-cools</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 01:21:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西门子价值 30 亿欧元的电机部门据称将吸引 Nidec 和 KPS 竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/nidec-kps-said-to-vie-for-siemens-s-3-billion-innomotics-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，日本电产株式会社和私募股权公司 KPS Capital Partners 正在竞相收购西门子股份公司的 Innotics 大型电机业务，这笔交易的售价可能约为 30 亿欧元（约合 33 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/nidec-kps-said-to-vie-for-siemens-s-3-billion-innomotics-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 01:08:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布莱克韦尔斯就 ValueAct 养老基金的角色质疑迪士尼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/blackwells-questions-disney-on-valueact-pension-management-role</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Blackwells Capital 认为，华特迪士尼公司应该披露 ValueAct Capital Management 正在管理其部分养老基金资产，这会加剧这两家激进投资公司在这家娱乐巨头追求不同议程时之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/blackwells-questions-disney-on-valueact-pension-management-role</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 00:28:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
